WEBVTT

00:00.944 --> 00:02.601
Previously on Gotham...

00:03.812 --> 00:05.383
- Bruce Wayne?
- No.

00:05.476 --> 00:06.609
But you could be.

00:07.306 --> 00:10.409
They've done a wonderful
job erasing the scars.

00:10.502 --> 00:12.146
- Are you prepared?
- Yes.

00:12.171 --> 00:14.283
But I still don't understand
how I can help save Gotham.

00:14.308 --> 00:16.079
You're only part of the plan.

00:16.142 --> 00:18.450
You know what must happen

00:18.520 --> 00:19.453
if he refuses.

00:19.521 --> 00:21.589
No one refuses the Court.

00:21.657 --> 00:23.758
- You lied to me.
- I didn't tell you the truth.

00:23.825 --> 00:25.214
- It's the same thing.
- Perhaps.

00:25.252 --> 00:26.737
But telling you your mother
was a con artist

00:26.786 --> 00:28.233
who'd only sought you out
for the purposes of

00:28.258 --> 00:31.655
getting money from me didn't seem like
a very attractive alternative.

00:33.502 --> 00:35.703
I don't love you.

00:35.771 --> 00:37.939
You need me, Edward Nygma!

00:38.006 --> 00:39.874
Just as I need you.

00:39.942 --> 00:41.475
You killed Isabella.

00:41.543 --> 00:43.377
I loved her, Oswald.

